<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6867439>
    dc:description "23. Tana River Mangabey (Cercocebus galeritus), 24. Agile Mangabey (Cercocebus agilis), 25. Golden-bellied Mangabey (Cercocebus chrysogaster), 26. Sanje River Mangabey (Cercocebus sanjer), 27. Sooty Mangabey (Cercocebus atys), 28. White-naped Mangabey (Cercocebus lunulatus), 29. Red-capped Mangabey (Cercocebus torquatus), 30. Mandrill (Mandnrillus sphinx), 31. Drill (Mandrillus leucophaeus), 32. Gray-cheeked Mangabey (Lophocebus albigena), 33. Rusty-mantled Mangabey (Lophocebus osmani), 34. Johnston's Mangabey (Lophocebus johnstoni), 35. Ugandan Crested Mangabey (Lophocebus ugandae), 36. Northern Black Crested Mangabey (Lophocebus aterrimus), 37. Southern Black Crested Mangabey (Lophocebus opdenboschi), 38. Kipunji (Rungwecebus kipunji)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6867439/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

